  "title": "Field Application Engineer (RF)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Work with contractors to deliver projects</li><li>Troubleshooting of issues and provide necessary remedial actions</li><li>Work with other stakeholders like customers and sales to understand gaps and propose solutions</li><li>Develop proof-of concepts methodology to ascertain concepts</li><li>Documenting and reporting of results</li><li>Able to work independently and as a team</li></ul><h2>Your qualifications</h2><ul><li>Diploma/Degree in Electrical/Electronics Engineering, Computer Science, or related</li><li>Previous experience on RF, satellite communications or networking will be an advantage</li><li>Ability to solve problems and adapt to new situations</li><li>Independent and proactive</li></ul><p>Interested candidates please apply/forward your resume to <strong>cecilia@achievasearch.com</strong><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/rohdeandschwarz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p><ul></ul>",
